RE Treys BdayThey do Thank you Im off to Vegas Fri but will speak to you all in the next couple of weeks Im sure Looks like xmas wont happen but I think well try and come down in the Spring Are there any good times for you guys Does Cameron get a Spring break Original Message From Cash Michelle mailtoMichelle NRONcom Sent Tuesday October PM To Subject RE Treys Bday DVDs would be good I got him the Godfather Trilogy but you might consider other movies He has Playstation so games are a good idea He always likes shortsleeved solid color polo shirts in size XL His Rice Owls baseball cap got mutilated when the baggage cart ran over his suitcase so he could use a replacement Anything with the theme would be fun Hope those ideas help Michelle Original Message From Brooks D Cash MD ENRON Sent Tuesday October PM To Cash Michelle Subject Treys Bday Any idease for the man who has everything Hope all is well there Eastern NC is interesting to say the least Sort of like Deleverance Brooks This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you winmaildat
